# CCO operator notes (Cloudflare BYO — not a local Postgres/Redis stack)
#
# Production secrets live in Cloudflare Secrets Store (provisioned at setup-c.co or Admin → Integrations).
# Per-user PCO OAuth tokens are encrypted in D1.
#
# Greenfield install: https://setup-c.co
# Day-two updates: Admin → Updates (Check / Apply) — churches do not git pull on Workers
# Operator docs: deploy/cloudflare/README.md
#
# Optional — contributors running install wizard locally (see docs/install/README.md):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_INSTALL_API_URL=http://localhost:8787
#
# Legacy VPS + Docker local dev: manual-vps branch only (not on main).
